data.description: Don't miss your chance to own this great townhome with a garage in Dundalk Highlands. As you walk in from the front sitting porch you find beautiful hardwood floors that lead from the comfortable living room, through an architectural archway, to the large dining room. The rear kitchen has a walkout to a fabulous backyard space. With its trees, ivy, and privacy you'll want to be out there every chance you get. A detached one-car garage is great for a car, motorcycle, or storage. Upstairs you'll find more of the classic hardwood floors in the hallway and the three bedrooms. The full bathroom is bright from its vintage skylight. Downstairs is unfinished but with its space and available plumbing for another bathroom it offers the potential to be a great space of your own design. It also has a rear walkout to add to the convenience. So don't delay, check out the photos and 3-D tour and make your appointment to see it now!
